вЂЄHow are you doing?

394
00:20:24.791 --> 00:20:27.166
вЂЄ-We're good.
вЂЄ-Uh-huh. [sniffs]

395
00:20:27.250 --> 00:20:29.250
вЂЄ-Hmm. Did you cook?
вЂЄ-Mmm.

396
00:20:29.333 --> 00:20:31.583
вЂЄ-Keep it down. You shouldn't be here.
вЂЄ-[Matipa] Shut up. Shut up.

397
00:20:31.666 --> 00:20:33.958
вЂЄ-You always make a noise when you come.
вЂЄ-[Matipa] Joyce!

398
00:20:34.041 --> 00:20:35.375
вЂЄ-Please calm down.
вЂЄ-Are you done?

399
00:20:35.875 --> 00:20:37.375
вЂЄ-Joyce!
вЂЄ-[Ntombi] Oh. my goodness.

400
00:20:37.458 --> 00:20:40.166
вЂЄ-Ma'am. I tried to calm her down.
вЂЄ-No. don't worry about it.

401
00:20:40.250 --> 00:20:41.333
вЂЄ-Don't worry.
вЂЄ-[Ntombi] Oh. gosh.

402
00:20:41.416 --> 00:20:42.833
вЂЄ[Joyce] I know how to deal with trash.

403
00:20:42.916 --> 00:20:43.916
вЂЄHey. hey. hey. hey. hey.

404
00:20:44.000 --> 00:20:47.291
вЂЄWhat is your problem? Why do you always
вЂЄmake a lot of noise in my house?

405
00:20:47.375 --> 00:20:50.208
вЂЄAw. Joycie. I thought we're family now.

406
00:20:50.291 --> 00:20:53.375
вЂЄWhat's mine is yours
вЂЄand what's yours is mine.

407
00:20:53.458 --> 00:20:54.916
вЂЄ[Joyce scoffs]

408
00:20:55.000 --> 00:20:56.625
вЂЄWhat do you want. Matipa?

409
00:20:57.625 --> 00:20:59.375
вЂЄI'm looking for our husband.

410
00:21:01.333 --> 00:21:03.291
вЂЄHis children needed him today.

411
00:21:04.416 --> 00:21:08.208
вЂЄ-But he decided to be a no-show.
вЂЄ-Huh?

412
00:21:09.000 --> 00:21:10.000
вЂЄ[chuckles]

413
00:21:10.541 --> 00:21:12.458
вЂЄAre things falling apart for you?

414
00:21:12.541 --> 00:21:17.416
вЂЄ[chuckling] Oh. wow.
вЂЄthere's trouble in paradise.

415
00:21:18.083 --> 00:21:19.958
вЂЄSo tell me. dear.

416
00:21:20.041 --> 00:21:24.375
вЂЄby telling the first wife
вЂЄabout this dilemma of yours.

417
00:21:24.458 --> 00:21:26.666
вЂЄtell me what do you
вЂЄwant me to do about it?

418
00:21:26.750 --> 00:21:27.750
вЂЄHmm?

419
00:21:27.833 --> 00:21:29.916
вЂЄ-You just love putting on a show.
вЂЄ-[chuckling]

420
00:21:30.000 --> 00:21:31.250
вЂЄ-I see that.
вЂЄ-[chuckling]

421
00:21:31.333 --> 00:21:34.000
вЂЄ-Let me tell you something. first wife.
вЂЄ-Mm-hmm.

422
00:21:35.250 --> 00:21:38.625
вЂЄYou forget that I know
вЂЄwhat type of woman you are.

423
00:21:39.208 --> 00:21:41.291
вЂЄYou're the blackmailing type.

424
00:21:41.375 --> 00:21:43.500
вЂЄ-Oh. okay.
вЂЄ-So maybe that's exactly what you did.

425
00:21:43.583 --> 00:21:44.708
вЂЄOh?

426
00:21:44.791 --> 00:21:47.083
вЂЄYou blackmailed him to stay with you.

427
00:21:47.166 --> 00:21:51.208
вЂЄ-Oh?
вЂЄ-You hate the fact that Jonasi chose me.

428
00:21:51.291 --> 00:21:53.750
вЂЄHe chose you? You're the chosen one?

429
00:21:53.833 --> 00:21:56.875
вЂЄ-My goodness. Forgive me. chosen one.
вЂЄ-[sighs]

430
00:21:56.958 --> 00:22:01.041
вЂЄPlease do me a favor.
вЂЄOpen your eyes and stop being an idiot.

431
00:22:01.791 --> 00:22:04.083
вЂЄDo you see your husband here? Huh?

432
00:22:04.166 --> 00:22:07.333
вЂЄIs Jonasi in this house?
вЂЄOr maybe you put him on my head?

433
00:22:07.416 --> 00:22:09.250
вЂЄDon't come here with that nonsense.

434
00:22:09.333 --> 00:22:11.375
вЂЄAnd do me one more favor. Matipa.

435
00:22:11.458 --> 00:22:15.000
вЂЄWhen you find that man of yours.
вЂЄlet him know I'm also looking for him.

436
00:22:15.083 --> 00:22:16.958
вЂЄHe needs to explain where he was today.

437
00:22:17.041 --> 00:22:19.666
вЂЄBecause he was meant to be
вЂЄat Nkazi's recital.

438
00:22:19.750 --> 00:22:21.875
вЂЄSomething I told him about months ago!

439
00:22:25.000 --> 00:22:26.583
вЂЄ[exhales sharply]

440
00:22:28.750 --> 00:22:30.166
вЂЄ[Essie] So. how are things?

441
00:22:31.750 --> 00:22:33.416
вЂЄIs the new wife treating you well?

442
00:22:33.500 --> 00:22:35.750
вЂЄ-[sighs]
вЂЄ-Is it that bad?

443
00:22:35.833 --> 00:22:38.750
вЂЄI don't know where to start. [scoffs] Wow.

444
00:22:39.291 --> 00:22:40.833
вЂЄ-[Essie scoffs]
вЂЄ-Mmm.

445
00:22:41.333 --> 00:22:42.625
вЂЄMmm!

446
00:22:42.708 --> 00:22:44.916
вЂЄ-Wow. My goodness.
вЂЄ-Jonasi.

447
00:22:45.000 --> 00:22:46.291
вЂЄ-It's delicious.
вЂЄ-[chuckles]

448
00:22:46.375 --> 00:22:48.125
вЂЄ-Mmm. Mmm.
вЂЄ-Is this how you eat now?

449
00:22:48.208 --> 00:22:49.208
вЂЄI'm hungry.

450
00:22:49.291 --> 00:22:50.666
вЂЄ-Wow.
вЂЄ-[Jonasi] Mmm.

451
00:22:50.750 --> 00:22:53.583
вЂЄWhy are you eating like a homeless person
вЂЄwhile you have a new wife?

452
00:22:53.666 --> 00:22:56.208
вЂЄ-Don't they cook at home?
вЂЄ-[chuckling]

453
00:22:56.291 --> 00:22:57.666
вЂЄ[Essie chuckles] Goodness.

454
00:22:57.750 --> 00:22:59.041
вЂЄI was really hungry.

455
00:22:59.625 --> 00:23:01.708
вЂЄOh. Please put it away.

456
00:23:01.791 --> 00:23:03.416
вЂЄ[Matipa] So you're telling meвЂ¦

457
00:23:04.916 --> 00:23:06.750
вЂЄhe disappeared on the both of us?

458
00:23:07.250 --> 00:23:08.541
вЂЄ[dramatic music playing]

459
00:23:10.291 --> 00:23:11.708
вЂЄLooks like it.

460
00:23:25.166 --> 00:23:26.333
вЂЄThis guy is here?

461
00:23:28.666 --> 00:23:31.166
вЂЄ[both breathing heavily]

462
00:23:31.250 --> 00:23:34.166
вЂЄ-Yes. [grunts] Yes.
вЂЄ-[moaning]

